data.description: This home has the option to ASSUME their VA loan at a 2.75% rate!!! No need to be a servicemember to qualify!  Contact the Co-list for further information. Welcome home to this ''have it all'' type of home in beautiful Wittman. This home sits on an acre with NO HOA and has owned solar, well water and on septic. Enjoy your very own private pool and slide every summer with friends and family! Large primary suite that has it's own living quarters and an oversized bathroom. For convenience the spare bathroom down the hall connects to the outside for easy access from the pool.  You don't want to miss out on this amazing deal of a lifetime.
